full_threads.body:
Hi there,

I'd like to request a couple of changes for our website.

  1. Hot topics page: https://msra.org.au/research-news-hot-topics/
    1. "AHSCT" is larger then other blocks. Please amend to be same height as diet and exercise and vitamin d.
    2. Could you please format the page https://msra.org.au/news/unravelling-causes-ms/ to be the same format as https://msra.org.au/medicinal-cannabis-ms/
    3. We would like to have the hot topics added to another drop down section in our menu bar. Please keep where it is but also add it to: FOR PEOPLE WITH MS. It can go underneath "COVID-19 and MS"

Please let me know if there are any questions regarding the above changes.

Kind regards,
Jess
